<section class="bg-white text-slate-900 py-20 lg:py-28 border-t border-slate-200">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-6xl">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-14 text-center lg:text-left">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold mb-4">
        What happens during the consultation
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto lg:mx-0">
        This is not a sales call. It’s a working session to determine whether building
        a client acquisition system makes financial sense for your business.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Steps -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">

      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">
          Step 1
        </p>
        <h3 class="font-medium text-lg mb-2">
          Understand your numbers
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          We look at your average ticket, margins, capacity, and constraints to
          understand what acquisition can realistically support.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">
          Step 2
        </p>
        <h3 class="font-medium text-lg mb-2">
          Identify where demand leaks
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          We map where prospects drop off — messaging, routing, tracking, follow-up —
          and what should be fixed before spending more.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">
          Step 3
        </p>
        <h3 class="font-medium text-lg mb-2">
          Decide the next logical step
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          If it makes sense to build, we’ll outline what that would involve.
          If it doesn’t, we’ll tell you — clearly.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Closing -->
    <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-slate-200 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
      <p class="text-slate-700 max-w-2xl">
        The goal is clarity. Not everyone who applies should move forward — and that’s intentional.
      </p>

      <a
        href="/apply"
        class="inline-block text-sm font-medium text-white bg-slate-900 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-800 transition"
      >
        Apply for a Consultation →
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
